---
title: Sweet Chilli Marinated Pork with pan fried broccolini and carrot
description: Fragrant rice forms the base of this Asian-inspired pork dish. Garlic, ginger and coriander are all familiar flavours in South-Asian cooking, while vibrant veg adds a satisfying crunch as well as all-important nutrients.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W42_IE_IEXQCLP16795-2_Main_high-f8c6f398.jpg
